                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). The prisoner was given into my custody—I told him the charge in English—I could not understand what he said—I received this pin (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) from Mr. Taylor</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
